X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>Join us for a free virtual session ahead of the In
 stitute for Curriculum and Campus Internationalization (ICCI) 2026. Led b
 y Dr. Susan B. Sutton\, this engaging event will feature ICCI alumni shar
 ing how their participation in the Institute has shaped and advanced inte
 rnationalization efforts at both the campus and curricular levels.<br />\
 n<br />\nParticipants will gain practical insights\, real-world examples\
 , and actionable strategies to support global learning and internationali
 zation at their own institutions. The session also offers an opportunity 
 to connect with colleagues and begin engaging with key ICCI themes before
  the Institute begins.<br />\n<br />\nNo ICCI registration required. For 
 more information\, visit <a title="https://icci.indiana.edu/program/index
 .html" href="https://icci.indiana.edu/program/index.html" data-auth="NotA
 pplicable" data-linkindex="0" data-ogsc="" data-olk-copy-source="MessageB
 ody">https://icci.indiana.edu/program/index.html</a></p>
X-LIVEWHALE-TAGS:Online
